&lt;h2&gt;Job Summary&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Compliance Manager to define, implement, and scale security and compliance frameworks spanning our global lab environments. This role will focus on securing sensitive hardware, enforcing access controls, and ensuring engineering data and infrastructure meet required compliance standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will play a meaningful role in enabling secure AI hardware development by establishing robust processes around lab zoning, asset tracking, and network segmentation while partnering with engineering teams across multiple locations.&lt;/p&gt;
